1
00:02:16,330 --> 00:02:18,390
为何那么久还未到？
Why are we not there yet?

2
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:22,000
你不要这样，糖吃完就会到
Don't be like that. We'll be there when you finish your candy.

3
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,200
这糖已是第八粒，骗人的
This is already my eighth piece. You tricked me.

4
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:33,200
爸爸，何时才到？
Dad, when will we get there?

5
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,340
多吃一粒糖
Have another caramel.

6
00:02:36,020 --> 00:02:37,680
转了这个弯，就到了
Once we go around this bend, we'll be there.

7
00:02:42,850 --> 00:02:43,739
这儿的空气很清新
The air here is so fresh.

8
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:44,850
最适合妈咪养病
It's the perfect place for Mom to recover.

9
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:52,346
那个是谁
Who's that?

10
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:54,560
邮差叔叔，一定很快就到
It's the postman. He'll be here in a minute.

11
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:58,670
邮差叔叔，你好吗！
Hello, Mr. Postman!

12
00:03:01,633 --> 00:03:02,856
我是大卷草子！你好吗？
I'm Kusakabe Satsuki! How do you do?

13
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:04,100
请多多指教
Pleased to meet you.

14
00:03:17,443 --> 00:03:18,276
次子，坐稳
Mei, hold on tight.

15
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,420
这儿有很多弯角
There are lots of twists and turns here.

16
00:03:19,490 --> 00:03:21,120
好晕呀，好晕呀
I'm so dizzy! So dizzy!

17
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,000
你好，小朋友
Hello there, little one.

18
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,526
你家人在家吗？
Is anyone from your family home?

19
00:03:34,610 --> 00:03:36,200
他们在对面干活
They're working across the road.

20
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:38,110
多谢你
Thank you.

21
00:03:40,510 --> 00:03:42,110
大家好吗？
How are you, everyone?

22
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:44,340
我是刚刚搬来的大卷
I'm Kusakabe. We just moved here.

23
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:46,510
请多多指教
It's a pleasure to meet you.

24
00:03:51,617 --> 00:03:52,506
女儿人家都不害羞
Girls shouldn't be so shy.

25
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,590
和你很熟络吗
Do you know him that well?

26
00:03:54,290 --> 00:03:55,290
多谢你
Thank you.

27
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:08,300
哈⋯我搔你痒⋯搔你痒⋯哈⋯
Ha… Tickle, tickle… Ha…

28
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:19,366
我们终于到了
We're finally here.

29
00:04:19,450 --> 00:04:20,450
真好！
This is great!

30
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:21,980
呀⋯等等我呀⋯
Oh… wait for me…

31
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:23,620
不用那么心急
Don't be in such a hurry.

32
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,346
这条河好美呀
This river is so beautiful.

33
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:27,430
是呀！
Yeah!

34
00:04:29,330 --> 00:04:30,330
你见到有鱼吗？
Do you see any fish?

35
00:04:31,130 --> 00:04:32,346
为何我看不见？
Why can't I see them?

36
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,870
你的近视眼，小心戴眼镜呀
You're so nearsighted. Be careful with your glasses.

37
00:04:35,770 --> 00:04:36,882
小心，不要掉下河呀！
Careful! Don't fall into the river!

38
00:04:38,940 --> 00:04:39,940
先看看屋子漂不漂亮
Let's see if the house is pretty first.

39
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:46,440
让一让，让一让，我先看呀！
Move over, move over! I want to look first!

40
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:48,640
好漂亮呀，过去看看
It's so pretty. Let's go over there.

41
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:51,010
哈⋯哈⋯真好！⋯哈⋯
Ha… ha… this is great!… ha…

42
00:04:52,850 --> 00:04:53,850
快点
Hurry up!

43
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:11,730
那么残旧，像是鬼屋
Looks like a haunted house!

44
00:05:12,753 --> 00:05:13,586
哈！真好
Ha! This is great!

45
00:05:13,670 --> 00:05:14,670
真好！够刺激呀
This is great! It's exciting!

46
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,770
那么儿戏，像是快塌下来
It looks so flimsy, like it could collapse any minute.

47
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,000
真好！
That's great!

48
00:05:47,910 --> 00:05:51,900
次子，你看看那棵树⋯
Mei, look at that tree…

49
00:05:52,910 --> 00:05:53,940
好高好大呀，看看
It's so tall and huge. Look!

50
00:05:55,020 --> 00:05:56,866
爸爸说我们小朋友的成就
Dad says when we grow up,

51
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:58,650
日后要像这棵树那样
we should become like that tree

52
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,390
那么高大呀！
and grow big and tall!

53
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,060
爸爸呀，这棵是什么树？
Dad, what kind of tree is this?

54
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,146
是橡树！
It's an oak tree!

55
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:15,290
橡树？
An oak tree?

56
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:17,900
大笨象变的树吗？
A tree that turned into a big elephant?

57
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:28,980
小心点！
Watch out!

58
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:32,650
有粒种子呀！
An acorn!

59
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,576
姐姐，给我看看！
Satsuki, let me see!

60
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:37,780
不给，不给，不给！
No, no, no!

61
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,160
追到请你吃鸡腿
If you catch me, I'll buy you a chicken leg!

62
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:45,790
我也找到只鸡腿
I found a drumstick too!

63
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:54,570
鸡腿？在这里怎会有鸡腿？
Chicken drumsticks? Why would there be chicken drumsticks here?

64
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,480
这些！
These!

65
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:58,670
我捡到粒种子，爸爸
I found a seed, Daddy.

66
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,370
我也捡到一粒呀
I found one too!

67
00:07:05,490 --> 00:07:08,110
种子？在屋里怎会有种子？
Seeds? How could there be seeds in the house?

68
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,450
是！为何会这样？
Yes! How could that happen?

69
00:07:11,020 --> 00:07:12,820
可能是松鼠搬进来的
Maybe some squirrels moved in.

70
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:15,090
松鼠懂得搬屋吗？
Do squirrels know how to move house?

71
00:07:16,130 --> 00:07:17,790
先生，这些东西搬到那里？
Sir, where should I put these?

72
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:20,760
对不起，请搬进来，得罪了
Excuse me, please bring them in. Sorry for the trouble.

73
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,652
快点去打开后门透透气
Hurry and open the back door to let some air in.

74
00:07:23,993 --> 00:07:24,826
乖乖的快点去
Be a good girl and hurry up.

75
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:25,930
来呀⋯来呀⋯来呀
Come on… come on… come on…

76
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:27,122
这两个小妹妹，很聪明
These two little girls are very clever.

77
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:31,880
快点来吧
Come on, hurry up.

78
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:33,380
追我呀，追我呀
Catch me! Catch me!

79
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:36,210
哈！⋯来呀⋯来呀⋯来呀⋯
Ha!… Come on… come on… come on…

80
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,846
⋯开！
Open it!

81
00:07:45,930 --> 00:07:46,930
先看看
Let's have a look first.

82
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:09,240
呀⋯
Ah…

83
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:14,710
唔，没问题！
Mm, no problem!

84
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:19,860
爸爸说，见到鬼怪就要靠吓
Dad says if you see ghosts, you have to scare them away.

85
00:08:20,890 --> 00:08:22,576
不见了？
They disappeared?

86
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:23,660
去了哪儿？
Where'd they go?

87
00:08:26,970 --> 00:08:27,886
不见了？
They disappeared?

88
00:08:27,970 --> 00:08:29,160
去看看
Let's go look.

89
00:08:31,170 --> 00:08:32,930
是嘛，看看还有没有未走的
I see. Let's check if there are any left.

90
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:35,470
没有！
No!

91
00:08:37,610 --> 00:08:38,996
那边是浴室
The bathroom's over there.

92
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,510
刚才我们见到些鬼怪
We just saw some ghosts.

93
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:42,110
什么？
What?

94
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,080
那些鬼怪给我们两个吓倒
The two of us scared those ghosts away.

95
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:46,080
进了浴室那边，现在不见了
They went into the bathroom, and now they're gone.

96
00:08:47,190 --> 00:08:48,190
让我看看
Let me have a look.

97
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,500
见到吗？
Did you see them?

98
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,830
没有，那些只是煤屎
No, those were just soot sprites.

99
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:06,760
是煤屎，不是鬼怪？
Soot sprites, not ghosts?

100
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:09,330
你们刚在外面那么光进屋
You came in from that bright sunshine outside,

101
00:09:09,410 --> 00:09:10,410
所以眼花！
so your eyes were playing tricks on you!

102
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:18,740
告诉你们，当阳光晒进屋
I'm telling you, once the sunlight shines into the house,

103
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,550
什么鬼怪都会跑光的
all the ghosts and goblins run away.

104
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:23,050
见光就跑的！
They run the second they see the light!

105
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:30,460
煤炭屎鬼跑了，鬼怪全不见了
The soot sprites ran away, and all the ghosts are gone.

106
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:32,790
真好⋯哈⋯
That's great… Ha…

107
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:38,270
你们不要玩了，快点去做事
Stop playing around and get to work.

108
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,100
你们懂得上二楼吗？
Do you know how to get to the second floor?

109
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:45,196
快上二楼，将所有的窗打开
Hurry upstairs and open all the windows.

110
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,280
是！
Okay!

111
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:47,850
⋯我要去呀⋯
…I want to go too…

112
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:50,366
楼梯呀
The stairs!

113
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:51,450
楼梯呀
The stairs!

114
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:53,350
不是这里
Not here.

115
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,150
没有
Nope.

116
00:09:56,843 --> 00:09:57,676
没有
Nope.

117
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:58,760
楼梯呀
The stairs!

118
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:01,860
在哪儿？
Where are they?

119
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,560
在哪儿？
Where are they?

120
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:08,130
没有的
They aren't here.

121
00:10:18,810 --> 00:10:21,370
没有的，没有的
Not here, not here.

122
00:10:25,490 --> 00:10:26,490
会不会在这儿？
Could they be over here?

123
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:33,720
喂，找到了
Hey, I found it!

124
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,490
这么黑，会不会又有⋯
It's so dark. Do you think there might be…

125
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,740
煤炭屎？
soot sprites?

126
00:10:47,610 --> 00:10:48,610
什么声音？
What's that sound?

127
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:53,650
鸡腿？
A drumstick?

128
00:11:00,350 --> 00:11:03,690
煤炭屎鬼跑了
The soot sprites ran away.

129
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:24,940
用绝招
Use your secret weapon.

130
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,920
这么大胆戏弄我们两个
How dare you tease the two of us like that.

131
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,470
让我应付你
I'll take care of you.

132
00:11:53,970 --> 00:11:54,970
有煤炭屎鬼
There are soot sprites!

133
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,170
次子，快帮手
Mei, come help me!

134
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:10,606
来呀
Come on.

135
00:12:10,690 --> 00:12:11,690
好重的，小心点
It's heavy. Be careful.

136
00:12:12,830 --> 00:12:14,020
爸爸，爸爸
Dad! Dad!

137
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:15,690
屋里又有鬼怪
There are ghosts in the house again!

138
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:20,016
你打开窗就不用怕那些鬼怪
If you open the windows, you won't be scared of ghosts.

139
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:22,360
爸爸高大威猛，又英明神武
Dad is big and brave, and really amazing too.

140
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:26,310
糟糕！
Oh no!

141
00:13:12,850 --> 00:13:14,410
真好，我捉到
I got one!

142
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:32,560
爸爸 救命！
Daddy, help!

143
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:37,370
姐姐！姐姐！
Satsuki! Satsuki!

144
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,670
真是活泼可爱
You're so lively and adorable.

145
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,810
这位就是住在我们邻家的八婶
This is Granny from next door.

146
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,750
她好好人，快点叫人
She's very kind, so say hello.

147
00:13:47,490 --> 00:13:48,650
八婆，你好吗？
Hello, Granny.

148
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:50,520
我是草子呀
I'm Satsuki.

149
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:52,490
草子小姐，你好吗？
Hello, Miss Satsuki.

150
00:13:53,890 --> 00:13:55,716
你们提早搬进来
You moved in earlier than expected.

151
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:58,616
我没时间帮你们打扫
I didn't have time to help you clean up.

152
00:13:58,700 --> 00:13:59,930
真是不好意思
I'm so sorry.

153
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:02,870
你太客气了
You're too kind.

154
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:05,230
大家都是邻居
We're neighbors, after all.

155
00:14:05,310 --> 00:14:07,030
好应该互相帮助的
Of course we should help each other.

156
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:12,370
次子，你的手为何这么肮脏？
Mei, why are your hands so dirty?

157
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:14,240
我捉到煤炭屎鬼
I caught a soot sprite.

158
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:18,280
你看看你的脚
Look at your feet.

159
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,620
为何会这样？
How did they get like that?

160
00:14:25,230 --> 00:14:28,130
原来你们见到煤炭屎鬼
So you two saw soot sprites.

161
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:34,586
告诉你们，这儿有很多煤炭屎鬼
Let me tell you, there are lots of soot sprites here.

162
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,956
煤炭屎鬼？
Soot sprites?

163
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,956
那些飞来飞去，神出鬼没
The ones that fly around and pop in and out?

164
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,370
真是叫煤炭屎鬼？
They're really called soot sprites?

165
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:43,470
你不用怕，根据这儿的传说
You don't need to be scared. According to the stories around here,

166
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:45,996
只有乖的小朋友
only good children

167
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,550
才可以见到煤炭屎鬼的
can see soot sprites.

168
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:52,610
我小时候，也时常见到它们
When I was little, I used to see them all the time too.

169
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:57,176
我小时候，比你们还漂亮
When I was little, I was even prettier than you two.

170
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,780
这山区真是很特别
These mountains are a very special place.

171
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:02,990
煤炭屎鬼是不会伤害小朋友
Soot sprites won't hurt children.

172
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:06,090
只要你对它们微笑
As long as you smile at them,

173
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,690
它们会帮助你的
they'll help you.

174
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,616
甚至你有什么求它们
If there's anything you ask of them,

175
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:12,930
它们都会帮你的
they'll help you with that too.

176
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:18,280
你这样吓它
You'll scare them like that.

177
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:20,280
它们可能已经飞走了
They've probably flown away already.

178
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:22,040
我早说不用怕的
See? I told you there was nothing to be scared of.

179
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:24,036
我早说不用怕的
I told you there was nothing to be scared of.

180
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,240
那么大的煤炭屎鬼，你也不怕
You're not even scared of a soot sprite that big.

181
00:15:26,890 --> 00:15:28,180
你不用吓我
Don't try to scare me.

182
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:31,890
你半夜不要叫我起来陪你上厕
Then don't wake me up in the middle of the night to go to the bathroom with you.

183
00:15:34,190 --> 00:15:36,716
小朋友，真可爱
What adorable children.

184
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,420
拿些水回来，让我清洁地方
Go bring back some water so I can clean this place up.

185
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,616
好的，八婆
Okay, Granny.

186
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:41,960
真好，有水玩了
Yay, we get to play with water!

187
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,000
真好
Great!

188
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,936
来吧，快点来吧
Come on, hurry up!

189
00:15:58,020 --> 00:15:59,020
是
Yes, sir!

190
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:12,490
八婆呀，有水了
Granny, we've got water!

191
00:16:13,470 --> 00:16:16,200
继续打水，不要让它停止
Keep pumping! Don't let it stop!

192
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,840
是
Okay!

193
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:46,700
祖母⋯
Granny…

194
00:17:01,810 --> 00:17:02,736
原来是你
Oh, it's you.

195
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:03,870
你来找谁？
Who are you here to see?

196
00:17:05,080 --> 00:17:07,810
我⋯我⋯我⋯我来找祖母的
I-I-I came to see Granny.

197
00:17:09,890 --> 00:17:10,890
你祖母？
Your granny?

198
00:17:13,130 --> 00:17:14,130
拿著
Here, take this.

199
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:18,800
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

200
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:20,960
害羞仔
Scaredy-cat.

201
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:26,526
不要叫我害羞仔
Don't call me a scaredy-cat!

202
00:17:26,610 --> 00:17:28,440
特别在这么丑怪的女孩面前
Especially not in front of such an ugly girl!

203
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,310
真没礼貌
How rude!

204
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:42,280
你孙子真是害羞，像我小时候
Your grandson is so shy, just like I was when I was little.

205
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:46,060
他拿来的糯米团，很好屹
The rice cakes he brought are really good.

206
00:17:46,130 --> 00:17:47,560
和妈咪做的那些一样好屹
They're just as good as the ones Mom makes.

207
00:17:49,130 --> 00:17:50,130
那就多吃些
Then have some more.

208
00:17:52,013 --> 00:17:52,846
再见
Goodbye.

209
00:17:52,930 --> 00:17:55,490
再见
Goodbye.

210
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,000
多谢你，八婶
Thank you, Granny.

211
00:17:59,470 --> 00:18:00,840
再见，八婆
Goodbye, Granny.

212
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,620
这个地方，每一样东西
This place… everything here

213
00:18:49,690 --> 00:18:51,210
都好像充满生命
feels so full of life.

214
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:18,650
风吹得像鬼叫，很恐怖
The wind sounds like ghosts howling. It's scary.

215
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:23,550
傻瓜，风不用怕
Silly, there's nothing to be afraid of. It's only the wind.

216
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:01,206
八婶说见到怕的东西
Granny says when you see something scary,

217
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:02,350
对它微笑就没事的
if you smile at it, you'll be all right.

218
00:20:05,260 --> 00:20:06,630
你大笑即是很害怕
If you're laughing that hard, it means you're really scared.

219
00:20:08,570 --> 00:20:09,630
你也怕吗？
Are you scared too?

220
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:16,840
不要呀，我怕搔痒的
No, don't! I'm ticklish!

221
00:20:53,710 --> 00:20:57,036
踩呀⋯
Pedal!

222
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,780
爸爸继续努力
Keep it up, Dad!

223
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:06,760
来了，知道吗
Here it comes, okay?

224
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,190
好了，大功告成
All right, that's all done.

225
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:09,093
我们去探妈咪
We're going to see Mom.

226
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,190
真好
That's great.

227
00:21:13,130 --> 00:21:14,390
去医院探妈咪
We're going to the hospital to see Mom.

228
00:21:16,370 --> 00:21:17,370
来了
Here it comes!

229
00:21:18,170 --> 00:21:19,230
好了，我们起程啦
All right, let's get going.

230
00:21:37,690 --> 00:21:41,290
八婆，你好吗？
Granny, how are you?

231
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:43,680
八婶，我们出去
Granny, we're heading out.

232
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:46,290
你们去哪儿？
Where are you going?

233
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:49,430
我们去医院探妈咪
We're going to visit Mom in the hospital.

234
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:52,570
问医生她何时可以出院
To ask the doctor when she can leave

235
00:21:53,370 --> 00:21:55,000
回家休养？
and come home to rest?

236
00:21:55,570 --> 00:21:57,010
好，再见
All right, goodbye.

237
00:22:13,690 --> 00:22:14,720
那儿呀
Over there!

238
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:15,790
那儿呀
Over there!

239
00:22:30,710 --> 00:22:32,940
爸爸，那儿就是医院了
Daddy, that's the hospital.

240
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:43,536
姨姨，你好吗？
Hello, Auntie. How are you?

241
00:22:43,620 --> 00:22:44,620
来探妈咪
We came to visit Mom.

242
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,720
妈咪
Mom!

243
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,680
次子，你乖吗？
Mei, have you been good?

244
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:52,160
爸爸说我此姐姐乖
Dad says Satsuki and I have been good.

245
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:54,460
真的？草子
Really, Satsuki?

246
00:22:55,230 --> 00:22:56,500
妈咪，你精神很好
Mom, you look really well.

247
00:22:57,140 --> 00:22:58,140
是吗？
Do I?

248
00:22:58,240 --> 00:23:00,400
爸爸和医生商量你出院的事
Dad's talking to the doctor about when you can leave the hospital.

249
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:02,540
是呀，我就快可以出院
Yes, I should be able to leave the hospital soon.

250
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:04,940
新屋好吗？
How's the new house?

251
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,440
你们执拾好东西吗？
Have you unpacked everything?

252
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:14,140
傻瓜，不要疑神疑鬼
Silly, don't be so jumpy.

253
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,590
妈咪，你怕煤炭屎鬼吗？
Mom, are you scared of soot sprites?

254
00:23:17,190 --> 00:23:19,660
心里没鬼怪，又怎会见到鬼怪呢
If there's nothing to fear in your heart, then you won't see any ghosts.

255
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:21,590
是呀
Yeah.

256
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,876
我们希望你的肺炎快点康复
We hope your pneumonia gets better soon

257
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:25,960
可以回家
so you can come home.

258
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,886
真是那么挂念妈咪
You really miss Mom that much?

259
00:23:27,970 --> 00:23:29,116
是呀
Yeah.

260
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,290
我挂念你多些
I miss you even more.

261
00:23:32,970 --> 00:23:33,926
次子的头发
Mei's hair…

262
00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:35,300
是你帮她梳的吗，草子？
Did you comb it for her, Satsuki?

263
00:23:36,980 --> 00:23:39,540
真棒，有进步
Very nice. You've improved.

264
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:42,710
不过姐姐时常骂我
But Satsuki always scolds me.

265
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:44,440
谁叫你不听话
That's because you won't behave.

266
00:23:45,020 --> 00:23:46,406
草子
Satsuki,

267
00:23:46,490 --> 00:23:47,806
过来
come here.

268
00:23:47,890 --> 00:23:49,406
为何将头发剪得那么短？
Why did you cut your hair so short?

269
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:50,650
我喜欢
I like it.

270
00:23:51,390 --> 00:23:52,506
我也要梳呀
I want mine brushed too!

271
00:23:52,590 --> 00:23:53,590
你等一会儿
Wait a minute.

272
00:23:54,290 --> 00:23:55,780
好了，不要整天争著
All right, stop fussing all the time.

273
00:23:56,600 --> 00:23:58,220
让我帮姐姐梳完才和你梳好吗？
Let me finish brushing Satsuki's hair, then I'll do yours, okay?

274
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,420
我长大之后
When I grow up,

275
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:02,360
头发是不是和妈咪一样？
will my hair be like yours, Mom?

276
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:06,130
会，因为你样子像妈咪
It will, because you look like me.

277
00:24:25,420 --> 00:24:26,754
爸爸，妈咪好像康复了很多
Dad, Mom seems a lot better.

278
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:28,546
是呀，没错
Yes, that's right.

279
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:30,390
医生说她很快就可以出院回家
The doctor said she'll be able to leave the hospital and come home soon.

280
00:24:31,430 --> 00:24:32,490
是不是明天
Will it be tomorrow?

281
00:24:33,670 --> 00:24:34,830
傻瓜，怎会那么快
Silly, not that soon.

282
00:24:35,940 --> 00:24:37,130
最快也要下星期
The soonest will be next week.

283
00:24:38,040 --> 00:24:41,030
妈咪出院后，我要妈咪抱著我睡
After Mom comes home, I want her to hold me while I sleep.

284
00:24:41,570 --> 00:24:42,956
你不是说你长大了
Didn't you say you were all grown up?

285
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:44,840
不用人陪你睡觉，忘记了？
That you didn't need anyone to sleep with you anymore, remember?

286
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:47,092
给我淘气多天都可以嘛
Can't I be naughty for a few more days?

287
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:12,200
懒惰爸爸，起床啦
Lazy Dad, wake up!

288
00:25:16,810 --> 00:25:18,500
懒惰爸爸，起床啦⋯
Wake up, sleepy Dad…

289
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:27,006
乱七八糟
What a mess.

290
00:25:27,090 --> 00:25:28,310
我什么都弄好了
I've got everything ready.

291
00:25:28,890 --> 00:25:30,380
我忘记了煮饭给你带回学校
I forgot to make your lunch to take to school.

292
00:25:30,890 --> 00:25:32,520
我已经煮好了，你不用担心
I've already made it, so don't worry.

293
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:34,590
一阵烧焦味
Something smells burnt.

294
00:25:34,690 --> 00:25:39,490
你乱说，我煮的东西很好吃的
That's not true. What I cook is delicious.

295
00:25:41,100 --> 00:25:42,230
姐姐真棒
Satsuki, you're amazing.

296
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:44,500
你们真乖
You two are such good girls.

297
00:25:47,010 --> 00:25:48,630
次子，这个饭盒是你的
Mei, this lunch box is yours.

298
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:54,840
草子，上学啦
Satsuki, it's time for school!

299
00:25:55,810 --> 00:25:56,836
阿信找我
Shin's looking for me.

300
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:57,920
来了⋯
I'm coming!

301
00:26:01,050 --> 00:26:02,450
这么快就认识到朋友？
You made a friend already?

302
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:05,336
姐姐很受同学欢迎的
Big sis is really popular at school.

303
00:26:05,420 --> 00:26:09,590
他叫阿信，我上学啦
His name is Shin. I'm off to school!

304
00:26:12,330 --> 00:26:13,330
再见
Bye!

305
00:26:13,970 --> 00:26:15,460
路上要小心呀
Be careful on your way!

306
00:26:17,423 --> 00:26:18,256
早安，阿信
Morning, Shin.

307
00:26:18,340 --> 00:26:19,173
走快些
Hurry up.

308
00:26:19,257 --> 00:26:20,257
迟到了
We're late!

309
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:25,010
早安⋯
Morning…

310
00:26:33,490 --> 00:26:34,490
爸爸
Dad!

311
00:26:35,990 --> 00:26:37,150
我要出去呀
I'm going out!

312
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:39,550
记著，不要走那么远
Remember, don't go too far.

313
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,190
知道了
Okay!

314
00:27:04,980 --> 00:27:06,210
爸爸，有午餐吃吗？
Dad, is it lunchtime yet?

315
00:27:06,890 --> 00:27:10,010
刚刚吃完早餐又吃午餐，你傻了
We just finished breakfast. You're silly.

316
00:27:20,900 --> 00:27:22,700
先生，买花吗？
Sir, would you like to buy some flowers?

317
00:27:39,450 --> 00:27:40,450
这些是什么东西？
What are these things?

318
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:52,260
找水桶盛著它
Put it in a bucket.

319
00:27:55,830 --> 00:27:56,830
有了
There is.

320
00:28:00,670 --> 00:28:01,670
有洞的
It's got a hole in it.

321
00:28:15,650 --> 00:28:16,650
鸡腿？
Chicken?

322
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:23,916
One mOre　TWO mOre
One more! Two more!

323
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:26,186
Three mOre　FOUr mOre
Three more! Four more!

324
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:27,390
很多呀
There are so many!

325
00:28:27,470 --> 00:28:29,730
很多呀
There are so many!

326
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:38,940
池池喳⋯
Tweet, tweet…

327
00:28:39,010 --> 00:28:40,980
池池喳⋯
Tweet, tweet…

328
00:29:17,320 --> 00:29:18,320
不要走呀
Don't go!

329
00:29:21,050 --> 00:29:22,080
不要走呀
Don't go!

330
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:24,410
不要走呀
Don't go!

331
00:29:27,260 --> 00:29:28,590
不要走呀
Don't go!

332
00:29:40,752 --> 00:29:42,086
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

333
00:29:42,170 --> 00:29:43,504
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

334
00:29:43,588 --> 00:29:44,922
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

335
00:29:45,006 --> 00:29:46,340
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

336
00:30:14,945 --> 00:30:16,279
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

337
00:30:16,363 --> 00:30:17,196
池池喳⋯
Chitter chatter…

338
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:18,614
Bom Bom Bart
Bom Bom Bart

339
00:30:18,698 --> 00:30:19,748
池池喳⋯
Chitter chatter…

340
00:30:31,390 --> 00:30:32,390
不要走呀⋯
Don't go…

341
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:36,690
追呀⋯
Come on, let's chase it…

342
00:30:57,988 --> 00:30:59,766
快走呀，Bom Bom Bart
Come on, Bom Bom Bart!

343
00:30:59,850 --> 00:31:01,936
有只粉红色的怪物在追我们
A pink monster's chasing us!

344
00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:03,020
快点回去主人那儿
Let's hurry back to our master!

345
00:32:23,923 --> 00:32:24,756
我笃
I found you!

346
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,840
我笃
I found you!

347
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:31,040
好玩呀
This is fun!

348
00:32:32,810 --> 00:32:35,440
好像棉胎那么软的
It's soft, like a fluffy blanket.

349
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:44,410
你样子好像只大鸡腿呀
You look like a giant drumstick.

350
00:33:53,530 --> 00:33:55,890
你是森林之王龙猫吗？
Are you Totoro, the King of the Forest?

351
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:10,000
有人没刷牙呀
Somebody didn’t brush their teeth!

352
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:26,876
龙猫，我叫次子，我很喜欢你
Totoro, my name is Mei. I like you a lot.

353
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,080
我和你做个好朋友
Let's be good friends.

354
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:38,370
好吗？
Okay?

355
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:18,010
池池喳⋯
Chit-chat…

356
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,670
Bom Bom Bart⋯
Bom Bom Bart…

357
00:35:46,593 --> 00:35:47,426
就这样，再见
Well then, goodbye.

358
00:35:47,510 --> 00:35:48,530
再见
Goodbye.

359
00:35:51,410 --> 00:35:52,356
我回来了
I'm home!

360
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,140
回来了，原来这么晚了
Welcome back. It's so late already.

361
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:56,010
次子呢？次子去了哪儿？
Where's Mei? Where did Mei go?

362
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,580
刚才还在外面玩耍
She was just outside playing.

363
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,566
就到晚饭时间
It's already time for dinner.

364
00:36:00,650 --> 00:36:03,310
次子，次子呀
Mei! Mei!

365
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:06,960
次子
Mei!

366
00:36:10,130 --> 00:36:11,530
次子呀
Mei!

367
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:20,540
爸爸，次子的帽子在这儿呀
Dad, Mei's hat is over here!

368
00:36:36,860 --> 00:36:37,980
次子呀，次子
Mei. Mei.

369
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:47,200
次子起床呀
Mei, wake up!

370
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,100
你怎可以在这儿睡觉？
How can you sleep out here?

371
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:54,970
大鸡腿
Big drumstick.

372
00:36:55,470 --> 00:36:56,470
大鸡腿？
Big drumstick?

373
00:36:57,210 --> 00:36:58,470
大鸡腿呢？
Where's the big drumstick?

374
00:37:01,380 --> 00:37:02,380
你还在作梦？
Are you still dreaming?

375
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:05,010
我见到一只好像大鸡腿的的龙猫
I saw a Totoro that looked like a big drumstick.

376
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:07,540
龙猫，在漫画书里面才有的
Totoro? That's only in picture books.

377
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,520
真是有龙猫的
There really is a Totoro.

378
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:14,750
它全身都是毛，口是这样的
It was all furry, and its mouth was like this.

379
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:18,760
有只这么大，有只大些
One was this big, and one was bigger,

380
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:21,990
有只还更大的在睡觉呀
and there was an even bigger one sleeping.

381
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:27,100
原来在这儿
There you are.

382
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:30,870
地方不错，十足基地一样
This is a nice spot. It's just like a hideout.

383
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:32,573
爸爸呀
Dad,

384
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,010
次子说在这儿见到龙猫
Mei said she saw Totoro here.

385
00:37:35,450 --> 00:37:36,450
龙猫？
Totoro?

386
00:37:37,720 --> 00:37:39,240
来啦⋯
Come on…

387
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:46,520
等等我
Wait for me!

388
00:37:47,030 --> 00:37:48,190
等等我
Wait for me!

389
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:54,630
就在这儿？
Right here?

390
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,986
我刚才看见它在这儿睡觉
I just saw it sleeping here.

391
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:00,160
但这儿只有一条路
But there's only one path here.

392
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,270
次子，回来！
Mei, come back!

393
00:38:03,940 --> 00:38:05,200
次子，回来！
Mei, come back!

394
00:38:13,390 --> 00:38:14,390
龙猫呢？
Where's Totoro?

395
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:21,990
我没撒谎，我真是见到它
I'm not lying. I really saw him.

396
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,890
你们不相信我？
You don't believe me?

397
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:35,110
次子
Mei,

398
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,070
你们都不相信我
None of you believe me.

399
00:38:39,010 --> 00:38:40,696
爸爸和姐姐都相信你
Daddy and Satsuki both believe you.

400
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:42,270
你一定会见到这个森林的主人
You must have seen the guardian of this forest.

401
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,736
它叫龙猫
He's called Totoro.

402
00:38:44,820 --> 00:38:45,980
这儿的传说是这样说的
That's what the legend here says.

403
00:38:46,690 --> 00:38:48,135
不是每个小朋友都可见到它的
Not every child gets to see him.

404
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:51,720
你见到它，是会带来好运的
If you see him, it brings you good luck.

405
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:56,306
好了，我们不如到附近走走
All right, let's go for a walk nearby.

406
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:57,316
好呀
Okay!

407
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,946
看看有什么美丽风景
Let's see what beautiful scenery there is.

408
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:00,030
好呀
Okay!

409
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:11,010
骑牛牛很好玩
It's fun riding on Daddy's back.

410
00:39:12,310 --> 00:39:13,940
爸爸，快点
Come on, Dad!

411
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:15,710
爸爸，快点
Come on, Dad!

412
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:19,666
次子，你越来越重了
You're getting heavy, Mei…

413
00:39:19,750 --> 00:39:20,750
爸爸，看看那棵橡树
Dad, look at that camphor tree!

414
00:39:21,950 --> 00:39:22,950
好大棵呀
It's huge!

415
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:32,460
是这棵树了
It's this tree.

416
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:34,186
是这棵树了
It's this tree.

417
00:39:34,270 --> 00:39:35,486
是呀
Yeah.

418
00:39:35,570 --> 00:39:36,403
爸爸
Dad!

419
00:39:36,487 --> 00:39:37,827
爸爸，快点
Dad, hurry up!

420
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,870
我在这儿见到龙猫的
I saw Totoro here.

421
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,110
为何洞口不见了？
Why is the hole gone?

422
00:39:50,850 --> 00:39:51,850
是这棵吗？
Was it this tree?

423
00:39:53,850 --> 00:39:55,220
她说洞口不见了
She said the hole disappeared.

424
00:39:56,550 --> 00:39:57,920
不是时常可以看见的
You can't see it all the time.

425
00:39:58,590 --> 00:40:00,350
为什么？为什么见不到
Why? Why can't we see it?

426
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:03,650
乡下人说，不是时常见到的
People in the country say you can't see it all the time.

427
00:40:06,060 --> 00:40:07,460
除非⋯好运气的人
Only the lucky ones can…

428
00:40:09,970 --> 00:40:12,116
爸爸自小在这个森林长大
Daddy grew up in this forest when he was little.

429
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,200
好挂念这儿
I've missed it so much.

430
00:40:15,570 --> 00:40:17,510
希望妈妈她在这儿养病
I hope Mom can rest here and get well soon.

431
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,580
早点康复
Get better soon.

432
00:40:20,180 --> 00:40:21,770
这个大森林，充满了灵气
This big forest is full of spirit.

433
00:40:22,310 --> 00:40:23,510
我们好好的在这儿生活
If we live well here,

434
00:40:24,980 --> 00:40:26,350
这儿会为我们带来好运的
it'll bring us good luck.

435
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:29,306
来吧，和龙猫说再见吧
Come on, let's say goodbye to Totoro.

436
00:40:29,390 --> 00:40:30,606
要回家吃饭
It's time to go home and eat.

437
00:40:30,690 --> 00:40:33,406
次子，你一定会好好运气
Mei, you're sure to have good luck.

438
00:40:33,490 --> 00:40:34,750
你都会见到龙猫的
You'll see Totoro too.

439
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,230
立正
Attention!

440
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,816
我们向龙猫说再见
Let's say goodbye to Totoro.

441
00:40:39,900 --> 00:40:40,900
龙猫，再见
Goodbye, Totoro.

442
00:40:41,500 --> 00:40:42,900
龙猫，再见
Goodbye, Totoro.

443
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,956
看谁走得快
Let's see who gets there first.

444
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:47,800
爸爸骗人，等等我
Daddy, that's not fair! Wait for me!

445
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:49,826
爸爸
Daddy!

446
00:40:49,910 --> 00:40:50,743
快点
Hurry up!

447
00:40:50,810 --> 00:40:52,400
等等我
Wait for me!

448
00:40:58,120 --> 00:41:00,280
妈咪，今天次子见到龙猫
Mom, Mei saw Totoro today,

449
00:41:01,220 --> 00:41:03,050
爸爸说可以带来好运的
and Daddy said he'll bring us good luck.

450
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:12,190
希望妈咪你都好运，快点康复
Mom, I hope you'll have good luck too and get well soon.

451
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:39,689
你上学吧，我应付得来的
You go on to school. I can manage by myself.

452
00:41:39,773 --> 00:41:40,606
你要乖呀，再见
Be good, okay? Bye-bye.

453
00:41:40,690 --> 00:41:41,890
再见
Bye-bye.

454
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:45,720
害羞仔，你还不上学
Shy boy, shouldn't you be off to school?

455
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:47,900
快了
In a minute!

456
00:42:11,590 --> 00:42:12,590
心思不集中
Pay attention.

457
00:42:30,810 --> 00:42:33,000
次子，山吹老师
Mei, Miss Yamanuki.

458
00:42:34,010 --> 00:42:35,010
什么事？
What is it?

459
00:42:36,150 --> 00:42:37,170
我妹妹在外面
My little sister's outside.

460
00:42:38,620 --> 00:42:39,840
她妹妹⋯
Her little sister…

461
00:42:41,450 --> 00:42:42,450
看看⋯
Let's see…

462
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:45,920
八婆，她什么事
Granny, what's wrong with her?

463
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:48,446
次子她早上发脾气
Mei had a tantrum this morning.

464
00:42:48,530 --> 00:42:50,290
要来找姐姐一同上课
She insisted on coming to class with her sister.

465
00:42:51,660 --> 00:42:52,960
次子
Mei.

466
00:42:53,770 --> 00:42:55,760
你也知道爸爸今天要回大学
You know Dad has to go back to the university today.

467
00:42:56,370 --> 00:42:57,856
你应该乖乖的留在八婆家
You should be a good girl and stay at Granny's.

468
00:42:57,940 --> 00:42:58,940
不要胡叫
Don't make a fuss.

469
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:03,340
我还有两课要上
I still have two classes left.

470
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:05,270
而且八婆也很忙
And Granny is very busy too.

471
00:43:06,950 --> 00:43:09,470
是否次子也想上学读书？
Does Mei want to come to school too?

472
00:43:18,860 --> 00:43:20,760
好吧，八婆，我和山吹老师说说
All right, Granny. I'll go talk to Mr. Yamabuki.

473
00:43:27,170 --> 00:43:29,816
各位同学，草子妈妈进了医院
Class, Satsuki's mother is in the hospital,

474
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:31,186
她爸爸又要工作
and her father has to work.

475
00:43:31,270 --> 00:43:33,760
所以她妹妹今天和我们一同上课
So her little sister will be joining us in class today.

476
00:43:34,410 --> 00:43:35,410
是
Yes, ma'am.

477
00:43:41,780 --> 00:43:42,996
你在画什么？
What are you drawing?

478
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:44,210
是只龙猫
It's Totoro.

479
00:43:45,180 --> 00:43:47,710
你不可以这么嘈吵
You can't be so noisy.

480
00:43:56,430 --> 00:43:57,990
再见，再见
See you later!

481
00:44:02,030 --> 00:44:03,860
我不上课外活动了
I'm not going to club today.

482
00:44:04,740 --> 00:44:05,740
那明天见吧
See you tomorrow, then.

483
00:44:09,140 --> 00:44:10,570
走快一点，快下雨了
Hurry up. It's going to rain.

484
00:44:20,050 --> 00:44:21,420
糟糕，下雨了
Oh no, it's raining.

485
00:44:22,150 --> 00:44:23,150
好大雨
It's pouring.

486
00:44:24,560 --> 00:44:26,350
走快点，快点，次子
Hurry up, Mei!

487
00:44:32,460 --> 00:44:34,520
你真不小心，来吧
You're so clumsy. Come on.

488
00:44:38,870 --> 00:44:40,860
我好棒，跌倒都没哭
I didn't even cry when I fell. Aren't I good?

489
00:44:44,480 --> 00:44:45,480
今次真是麻烦
This really is a problem.

490
00:44:47,880 --> 00:44:50,540
土地公公，求你叫雨快点停止
Dear Lord Guardian, please make the rain stop soon.

491
00:45:35,730 --> 00:45:36,730
你⋯
But…

492
00:45:56,880 --> 00:45:58,350
姐姐，真是走运
That was lucky, wasn't it, Sis?

493
00:46:00,280 --> 00:46:01,480
不过伞子是破的
But this umbrella's got holes in it.

494
00:46:14,100 --> 00:46:15,330
爸爸出去时没拿伞子
Dad went out without his umbrella.

495
00:46:16,400 --> 00:46:17,560
我们去车站接他
Let's go meet him at the station.

496
00:46:21,310 --> 00:46:23,030
都说伞给吹破了，已丢了
I told you, the wind tore my umbrella and I threw it away.

497
00:46:23,710 --> 00:46:25,700
你很喜欢那伞子，怎会丢掉？
You liked that umbrella so much. Why would you throw it away?

498
00:46:27,480 --> 00:46:28,480
都说已经丢掉了
I said I already threw it away.

499
00:46:29,280 --> 00:46:30,896
明天给你买新的
I'll buy you a new one tomorrow.

500
00:46:30,980 --> 00:46:31,980
我不喜欢
I don't want one.

501
00:46:45,600 --> 00:46:46,820
请问有人吗？
Hello?

502
00:46:49,630 --> 00:46:52,600
原来是草子和次子，奶奶
Oh, it's Satsuki and Mei, Granny.

503
00:46:54,710 --> 00:46:56,326
今天真是麻烦你
Sorry to trouble you today.

504
00:46:56,410 --> 00:46:58,030
麻烦？我们没帮过你什么？
Trouble? We didn't help you with anything.

505
00:46:58,610 --> 00:47:00,510
有，害羞仔将伞子借给我们
We did. That shy boy lent us his umbrella.

506
00:47:01,810 --> 00:47:02,810
是吗？
He did?

507
00:47:02,910 --> 00:47:04,900
不用客气，只是破伞子吧
Don't mention it. It's just an old umbrella.

508
00:47:05,720 --> 00:47:06,880
因为当时雨很大
It was raining so hard then.

509
00:47:08,120 --> 00:47:09,480
幸好他将伞子借给我们
It really helped that he lent it to us.

510
00:47:10,120 --> 00:47:11,876
不过弄到他全身湿透
But he got completely soaked.

511
00:47:11,960 --> 00:47:13,076
不要紧
It's all right.

512
00:47:13,160 --> 00:47:15,576
那傻瓜整天都弄得全身湿透
That silly boy comes home soaked all the time anyway.

513
00:47:15,660 --> 00:47:16,660
才回家的
That's how he got home.

514
00:47:17,460 --> 00:47:18,746
你们现在去接爸爸放工？
Are you going to meet your father after work now?

515
00:47:18,830 --> 00:47:19,830
是
Yes.

516
00:47:19,930 --> 00:47:21,269
你真乖
You're such a good girl.

517
00:47:21,353 --> 00:47:22,186
再见
Goodbye.

518
00:47:22,270 --> 00:47:23,103
再见
Goodbye.

519
00:47:23,187 --> 00:47:24,187
再见
Goodbye.

520
00:47:34,550 --> 00:47:36,166
有客人来过吗？
Did someone come by?

521
00:47:36,250 --> 00:47:37,250
没有
No.

522
00:47:42,090 --> 00:47:43,090
有车到站
The bus is here.

523
00:47:56,770 --> 00:47:57,770
你们乘车吗？
Are you getting on?

524
00:48:00,200 --> 00:48:01,200
好了，开车
All right, drive on.

525
00:48:09,780 --> 00:48:11,040
爸爸没乘这巴士？
Dad wasn't on this bus?

526
00:48:12,320 --> 00:48:13,340
一定是乘下一班
He'll be on the next one for sure.

527
00:48:14,420 --> 00:48:15,580
你不如去八婆家
Why don't you go to Granny's house?

528
00:48:16,090 --> 00:48:17,090
不要
No.

529
00:48:53,020 --> 00:48:54,020
干什么？
What are you doing?

530
00:49:27,460 --> 00:49:29,120
次子，你累吗？
Mei, are you tired?

531
00:49:30,160 --> 00:49:33,560
刚才叫你去八婆家
I told you to go to Granny's a little while ago.

532
00:49:36,570 --> 00:49:38,160
车就快到，你多撑一会儿
The bus will be here soon, so hang in there a little longer.

533
00:49:45,070 --> 00:49:46,560
为何这部车那么久还没到？
Why is this bus taking so long?

534
00:49:55,290 --> 00:49:56,290
我背你
I'll carry you.

535
00:51:19,800 --> 00:51:20,890
龙猫？
Totoro?

536
00:51:31,180 --> 00:51:32,180
你等一会儿
Wait a second.

537
00:51:38,320 --> 00:51:39,320
借给你
You can borrow this.

538
00:51:41,090 --> 00:51:42,720
快点，次子就快掉下来
Hurry, Mei's about to fall off.

539
00:51:49,500 --> 00:51:50,500
是这样做的
You do it like this.

540
00:53:08,210 --> 00:53:09,210
车来了
Here comes the bus!

541
00:53:14,480 --> 00:53:15,480
什么东西？
What is it?

542
00:54:16,750 --> 00:54:18,870
龙猫拿了爸爸的伞子走呀
Totoro took Dad's umbrella!

543
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:34,360
你们来接我吗？
Did you come to meet me?

544
00:54:34,860 --> 00:54:35,860
爸爸
Dad!

545
00:54:36,870 --> 00:54:39,460
风大雨大，你们都来车站接我
With all this wind and rain, you came all the way to the station for me.

546
00:54:41,270 --> 00:54:42,569
你们真乖
You two are such good girls.

547
00:54:42,653 --> 00:54:43,486
见到了
I saw him!

548
00:54:43,570 --> 00:54:44,630
见到了，终于见到
I saw him! I finally saw him!

549
00:54:44,710 --> 00:54:46,680
龙猫，猫巴士呀
Totoro, and the Catbus!

550
00:54:48,510 --> 00:54:49,510
猫巴士？
The Catbus?

551
00:54:49,580 --> 00:54:50,600
好大的猫巴士呀
The Catbus was huge!

552
00:54:50,680 --> 00:54:54,580
真好，我终于见到龙猫
I'm so glad. I finally got to meet Totoro.

553
00:54:55,790 --> 00:54:57,150
真好
That's wonderful.

554
00:54:57,220 --> 00:54:58,950
真好，龙猫
How wonderful, Totoro.

555
00:54:59,020 --> 00:55:00,706
龙猫原来是这样的
So that's what Totoro looks like.

556
00:55:00,790 --> 00:55:01,790
真好
How wonderful.

557
00:55:03,290 --> 00:55:04,450
少见多怪
You're making a fuss over nothing.

558
00:55:23,550 --> 00:55:26,610
妈咪，我今晚终于见到龙猫
Dear Mom, tonight I finally saw Totoro.

559
00:55:27,320 --> 00:55:28,680
今晚真是不可思议
Tonight was really mysterious.

560
00:55:29,750 --> 00:55:31,980
可以说又可怕又开心
It was scary and fun at the same time.

561
00:55:34,560 --> 00:55:35,650
这龙猫还送了一个
Totoro even gave us

562
00:55:35,730 --> 00:55:37,220
用竹叶包的礼物给我们
a present wrapped in a bamboo leaf.

563
00:55:38,660 --> 00:55:39,820
回家后打开来看看
When we got home and opened it,

564
00:55:40,660 --> 00:55:42,460
原来全部都是橡树的果实
it turned out to be full of acorns.

565
00:55:48,340 --> 00:55:50,656
我们将果实种在后园
So we planted the acorns in the backyard,

566
00:55:50,740 --> 00:55:53,110
希望将来会变成一个橡树森林
hoping that someday it would turn into an oak forest.

567
00:55:53,840 --> 00:55:54,756
但是⋯
But…

568
00:55:54,840 --> 00:55:55,900
等呆了也不发芽
no matter how long we waited, they just wouldn't sprout.

569
00:55:56,850 --> 00:55:58,750
次子每天都望著泥土很失望
Every day Mei would stare at the dirt, looking so disappointed.

570
00:55:59,850 --> 00:56:01,540
都是我第一次见到她失望的表情
It was the first time I'd ever seen her look disappointed,

571
00:56:02,690 --> 00:56:04,210
我心都很不安乐
and it made me feel uneasy too.

572
00:56:11,460 --> 00:56:13,990
快要放暑假，希望你快点康复
Summer vacation is almost here. I hope you get well soon.

573
00:56:15,260 --> 00:56:17,060
你的大女儿，草子
Your eldest daughter, Satsuki.

574
00:56:26,780 --> 00:56:27,896
乖，要关灯
Come on, lights out.

575
00:56:27,980 --> 00:56:28,980
不要
No!

576
00:56:29,680 --> 00:56:31,940
爸爸，明天那些鸡腿会发芽吗？
Dad, will those drumsticks sprout tomorrow?

577
00:56:32,720 --> 00:56:33,896
我怎知道
How should I know?

578
00:56:33,980 --> 00:56:35,203
间龙猫吧，龙猫才知道嘛
Ask Totoro. Totoro would know.

579
00:56:36,790 --> 00:56:37,790
早点睡吧
Go to sleep now.

580
00:57:10,250 --> 00:57:11,380
池池喳⋯
Chit-chat…

581
00:57:11,450 --> 00:57:13,420
Bom Bom Bart⋯
Bom Bom Bart…

582
00:57:26,170 --> 00:57:27,290
喂，次子
Hey, Mei.

583
00:57:27,370 --> 00:57:28,815
Bom Bom Bart⋯
Bom bom bart…

584
00:57:28,899 --> 00:57:30,019
池池喳⋯
Chitty chatter…

585
00:57:32,480 --> 00:57:33,480
他们在干什么？
What are they doing?

586
00:57:45,890 --> 00:57:46,890
不如我们出去看看
Let's go outside and take a look.

587
00:59:18,250 --> 00:59:20,910
真好，成功了
Great, we did it!

588
00:59:21,450 --> 00:59:22,450
真好
Great!

589
00:59:36,170 --> 00:59:37,170
我也去
I'm going too.

590
00:59:51,480 --> 00:59:52,480
等等我呀
Wait for me!

591
01:00:38,130 --> 01:00:39,490
飞原来是这么好玩的
Flying is so much fun!

592
01:01:41,590 --> 01:01:42,590
树呢？
What about the tree?

593
01:01:47,783 --> 01:01:48,616
真棒
We did it!

594
01:01:48,700 --> 01:01:49,533
真棒
We did it!

595
01:01:49,617 --> 01:01:51,930
真棒
We did it!

596
01:01:52,000 --> 01:01:52,833
发芽了
They sprouted!

597
01:01:52,917 --> 01:01:53,750
发芽了
They sprouted!

598
01:01:53,834 --> 01:01:56,770
发芽了
They sprouted!

599
01:01:56,840 --> 01:01:59,570
发出芽了
They've sprouted!

600
01:02:03,533 --> 01:02:04,366
真棒
Wonderful.

601
01:02:04,450 --> 01:02:05,283
真棒
Wonderful.

602
01:02:05,367 --> 01:02:06,427
真棒
Wonderful.

603
01:02:06,511 --> 01:02:07,511
真棒⋯发出芽了⋯
Wonderful… They've sprouted…

604
01:02:17,730 --> 01:02:19,630
有人吗？收电报
Anybody home? Telegram!

605
01:02:21,930 --> 01:02:22,990
请问有人吗？
Excuse me, is anybody home?

606
01:02:24,370 --> 01:02:25,630
大卷先生，收电报呀
Mr. Kusakabe, telegram for you!

607
01:02:27,840 --> 01:02:28,840
为何没人的？
No one's home?

608
01:02:36,350 --> 01:02:37,570
八婆
Granny!

609
01:02:40,650 --> 01:02:41,650
八婆
Granny!

610
01:02:42,690 --> 01:02:43,690
是你们
Oh, it's you two.

611
01:02:46,160 --> 01:02:47,620
是呀，次子，你吃粟米吗？
Yes, Mei, would you like some corn?

612
01:02:57,070 --> 01:02:58,090
八婆，我想吃
Granny, I want one.

613
01:02:58,770 --> 01:02:59,770
好
All right.

614
01:03:06,310 --> 01:03:08,440
八婆，这块菜田像个宝山
Granny, this vegetable patch is like a treasure mountain.

615
01:03:10,780 --> 01:03:12,680
是呀，来！休息一会儿
Yes, come on! Let's take a little break.

616
01:03:19,990 --> 01:03:21,320
浸到很冰冻的
They're nice and cold now.

617
01:03:21,820 --> 01:03:22,820
我不客气了
Thanks for the food.

618
01:03:33,100 --> 01:03:34,416
很好屹
It's delicious.

619
01:03:34,500 --> 01:03:35,416
是呀
It sure is.

620
01:03:35,500 --> 01:03:37,670
因为这儿的阳光和泥土都很好
Because the sunshine and the soil here are so good,

621
01:03:38,240 --> 01:03:40,456
所以吃了对身体很有帮助的
they're very good for your body.

622
01:03:40,540 --> 01:03:41,700
那对妈妈的病呢？
Then will it help Mom get better too?

623
01:03:42,510 --> 01:03:43,640
当然有帮助
Of course it will.

624
01:03:44,150 --> 01:03:45,510
吃了八婆种的蔬菜
If she eats Granny's vegetables,

625
01:03:46,320 --> 01:03:47,836
会立即完全康复
she'll be all better in no time.

626
01:03:47,920 --> 01:03:50,080
妈咪星期六就会出院
Mom's coming home on Saturday.

627
01:03:50,720 --> 01:03:53,236
那时候我又可以撒妈咪的娇了
Then I can cuddle up and snuggle with Mom again.

628
01:03:53,320 --> 01:03:54,259
好了
Oh.

629
01:03:54,343 --> 01:03:55,176
好了
Oh.

630
01:03:55,260 --> 01:03:57,146
终于都可以出院了
So she's finally getting out of the hospital.

631
01:03:57,230 --> 01:03:58,780
她不是真的出院
She's not really being discharged.

632
01:03:59,360 --> 01:04:00,560
星期一还要回去的
She has to go back on Monday.

633
01:04:01,160 --> 01:04:02,760
是给她习惯一下
It's just to help her get used to things.

634
01:04:03,530 --> 01:04:06,660
那要她吃多些这儿的生果和蔬菜
Then she should eat lots of the fruit and vegetables here.

635
01:04:07,470 --> 01:04:09,960
次子摘的粟米要留给妈咪吃
We have to save the corn Mei picked for Mom.

636
01:04:11,340 --> 01:04:12,740
妈咪一定很开心
Mom will be so happy.

637
01:04:19,780 --> 01:04:20,940
你们有电报
You have a telegram.

638
01:04:22,050 --> 01:04:23,080
因为你们家里没有人
Since no one was home,

639
01:04:23,150 --> 01:04:24,380
所以送来我们这儿
they brought it to our place.

640
01:04:24,990 --> 01:04:25,866
是我们的？
For us?

641
01:04:25,950 --> 01:04:26,950
是呀
That's right.

642
01:04:29,760 --> 01:04:32,250
但是爸爸说要迟些才回来
But Dad said he wouldn't be back until later.

643
01:04:32,760 --> 01:04:34,890
打开来看看，可能有急事
You'd better open it, in case it's urgent.

644
01:04:39,570 --> 01:04:42,330
请尽快联络七国山
Please contact Shichikokuyama at once.

645
01:04:43,370 --> 01:04:44,586
是医院寄来的
It's from the hospital.

646
01:04:44,670 --> 01:04:45,940
是妈咪住的那间医院
It's Mom's hospital.

647
01:04:46,680 --> 01:04:48,040
是妈咪，不知道有什么事
It's about Mom. I wonder what's happened.

648
01:04:50,310 --> 01:04:52,540
婆，怎么办？怎样联络？
Granny, what should we do? How do we contact them?

649
01:04:53,120 --> 01:04:54,840
你冷静些，不要紧张
Calm down. Don't panic.

650
01:04:54,920 --> 01:04:56,320
你可以找到你爸爸吗？
Do you know where your dad is?

651
01:04:56,990 --> 01:04:58,320
我知研究室的电话
I know the number for his office.

652
01:04:58,390 --> 01:04:59,720
但是家里没有电话
But we don't have a phone.

653
01:05:00,403 --> 01:05:01,236
害羞仔
You shy boy.

654
01:05:01,320 --> 01:05:03,850
快带她去村长家借电话啦
Hurry and take her to the village headman's house to borrow the phone.

655
01:05:10,230 --> 01:05:11,530
次子，你不要跟姐姐去
Mei, don't go with Satsuki.

656
01:05:22,010 --> 01:05:24,040
次子，你快回去八婆那儿
Mei, hurry back to Granny's!

657
01:06:01,680 --> 01:06:05,410
请帮我接郊区，东京de
Hello, I'd like to make a long-distance call, please.

658
01:06:05,950 --> 01:06:08,950
地方区号码是1382，是
It's to Tokyo 31-1382.

659
01:06:11,690 --> 01:06:13,890
害羞仔，你女朋友真可爱
You shy boy, your girlfriend is so cute.

660
01:06:16,770 --> 01:06:22,086
这儿是⋯考古学研究室吗？
Is this… the archaeology department?

661
01:06:22,170 --> 01:06:23,170
请你叫⋯叫爸爸听⋯
Could I speak to my father…

662
01:06:23,670 --> 01:06:24,700
不是，是大卷先生
No, I mean Mr. Kusakabe.

663
01:06:26,063 --> 01:06:26,896
我是他女儿
I'm his daughter.

664
01:06:26,980 --> 01:06:27,980
草子呀，是
Kusakabe. Yes.

665
01:06:32,180 --> 01:06:33,340
爸爸呀，我是草子
Dad, it's me, Satsuki.

666
01:06:34,420 --> 01:06:35,710
草子，什么事
Satsuki, what is it?

667
01:06:36,573 --> 01:06:37,406
是
Yes.

668
01:06:37,490 --> 01:06:38,490
是
Yes.

669
01:06:39,090 --> 01:06:40,306
是医院呀？
Is it from the hospital?

670
01:06:40,390 --> 01:06:42,020
我知道了，我立即打电话去
I understand. I'll call right away.

671
01:06:43,030 --> 01:06:45,020
妈咪有事吗？那怎办，爸爸？
Did something happen to Mom? What are we going to do, Dad?

672
01:06:46,200 --> 01:06:47,316
你放心
Don't worry.

673
01:06:47,400 --> 01:06:49,130
我问完后打电话回来给你
I'll ask them and call you right back.

674
01:06:50,200 --> 01:06:51,200
你在这儿等我一会儿
Wait there for me a little while.

675
01:06:53,540 --> 01:06:54,830
草子，我现在挂线
Satsuki, I'm hanging up now.

676
01:06:58,310 --> 01:06:59,756
村长太太
Madam Mayor,

677
01:06:59,840 --> 01:07:01,926
我可以在这儿等爸爸电话吗
may I wait here for my dad's call?

678
01:07:02,010 --> 01:07:04,310
不要紧，你随便吧
Of course, make yourself at home.

679
01:07:11,920 --> 01:07:13,220
姐姐
Satsuki!

680
01:07:22,970 --> 01:07:25,430
不能给你，粟米是给我妈咪吃的
I can't give it to you. This corn is for my mom.

681
01:07:27,240 --> 01:07:29,400
不可以，我要给妈咪
No, I have to give it to my mom.

682
01:07:44,550 --> 01:07:45,850
姐姐
Satsuki,

683
01:07:46,690 --> 01:07:49,210
次子，妈咪现在的病情不太好
Mei, Mom's condition isn't very good right now.

684
01:07:49,290 --> 01:07:51,090
所以要迟些才可回家？
So she has to come home a little later?

685
01:07:53,100 --> 01:07:54,100
不要
No!

686
01:07:55,700 --> 01:07:56,930
妈咪身体要紧嘛
Mom's health comes first.

687
01:07:57,000 --> 01:07:58,860
你不要发脾气，你越来越不听话
Don't throw a tantrum. You're getting more and more disobedient.

688
01:07:59,570 --> 01:08:00,800
不要
No!

689
01:08:02,300 --> 01:08:03,900
你⋯你想妈咪死吗？
Y-You want Mom to die?

690
01:08:04,570 --> 01:08:05,730
我不要
I don't!

691
01:08:07,610 --> 01:08:09,470
干什么，只不过迟几天才回家
What's gotten into you? She's only coming home a few days later.

692
01:08:12,380 --> 01:08:14,040
你不乖，我不理你
If you won't behave, I'm not talking to you.

693
01:08:25,730 --> 01:08:26,820
你回去吧
You go on back.

694
01:08:32,730 --> 01:08:34,700
姐姐好衰的
Satsuki's so mean.

695
01:09:00,960 --> 01:09:02,400
我替你们收了衣服
I brought in the laundry for you.

696
01:09:05,270 --> 01:09:09,086
不要那么没心机，提起精神
Don't look so glum. Cheer up.

697
01:09:09,170 --> 01:09:10,470
八婆现在帮你们手
Granny's here to help you now.

698
01:09:16,480 --> 01:09:19,240
你爸爸都已经去了医院看她了
Your father's already gone to the hospital to see her.

699
01:09:20,780 --> 01:09:23,010
你妈咪不会有事的
Your mom's going to be fine.

700
01:09:23,990 --> 01:09:25,780
下星期六就会回家
She'll be home next Saturday.

701
01:09:27,260 --> 01:09:28,260
撒谎
That's a lie.

702
01:09:31,690 --> 01:09:33,090
上次又是这样说
That's what they said last time, too.

703
01:09:33,660 --> 01:09:35,250
只是去医院住两天
They said she'd only be in the hospital for two days.

704
01:09:35,760 --> 01:09:37,030
怎知道一住就住这么久
Who knew she'd end up staying so long?

705
01:09:39,400 --> 01:09:40,700
如果她死了，那怎么办？
But what if she dies?

706
01:09:42,570 --> 01:09:44,026
不会的，草子
She won't, Satsuki.

707
01:09:44,110 --> 01:09:45,400
万一妈咪她真是⋯
But what if Mom really…

708
01:09:50,310 --> 01:09:52,210
没事的，你放心吧
Don't worry, it'll be okay.

709
01:09:53,180 --> 01:09:54,696
有个那么可爱的女儿
With such a sweet little daughter,

710
01:09:54,780 --> 01:09:56,050
她又怎舍得死呢
how could she bear to die?

711
01:09:57,520 --> 01:10:00,606
不要哭，八婆在这儿陪你
Don't cry. Granny's here with you.

712
01:10:00,690 --> 01:10:03,450
陪到你爸爸回来，乖啦
I'll stay until your father comes back, all right?

713
01:10:48,640 --> 01:10:50,610
次子
Mei.

714
01:10:55,740 --> 01:10:57,300
次子
Mei!

715
01:11:05,790 --> 01:11:07,006
次子回来了吗？
Did Mei come back?

716
01:11:07,090 --> 01:11:08,720
没有，她还没有回来
No, she still hasn't come back.

717
01:11:10,860 --> 01:11:14,476
奇怪，究竟次子去了哪儿？
That's strange. Where could Mei have gone?

718
01:11:14,560 --> 01:11:16,120
会不会因为我刚才骂过她
Could it be because I scolded her just now

719
01:11:16,200 --> 01:11:18,786
不知道她会不会⋯
I wonder if she…

720
01:11:18,870 --> 01:11:20,770
去了妈咪住的那间医院？
went to the hospital where Mom is?

721
01:11:21,370 --> 01:11:22,670
她怎样去医院？
How could she get to the hospital?

722
01:11:23,270 --> 01:11:24,270
很远的
It's so far away.

723
01:11:24,770 --> 01:11:27,096
她这么小怎懂得乘车去医院
She's so little, how could she know how to get there by bus?

724
01:11:27,180 --> 01:11:28,180
我去找她
I'll go look for her.

725
01:11:29,780 --> 01:11:33,010
害羞呀，快去找你爸爸帮手
Don't be shy, hurry and go get your dad's help.

726
01:11:33,780 --> 01:11:36,180
次子失踪了？
Mei's missing?

727
01:11:45,990 --> 01:11:47,316
次子，糟糕
Mei, oh no.

728
01:11:47,400 --> 01:11:48,950
她时常都会迷失路的
She always gets lost.

729
01:11:56,300 --> 01:11:58,970
次子，次子
Mei, Mei!

730
01:12:05,210 --> 01:12:07,270
伯伯，有事请问你
Excuse me, sir, may I ask you something?

731
01:12:08,020 --> 01:12:10,110
见到有个梳孖辫的小女孩经过吗
Have you seen a little girl with pigtails come by?

732
01:12:10,950 --> 01:12:11,950
她是我妹妹
She's my sister.

733
01:12:13,620 --> 01:12:15,950
不见，我在这儿都大半天
No, I haven't. I've been here most of the day.

734
01:12:16,020 --> 01:12:17,080
不见有小女孩经过
I haven't seen any little girl come by.

735
01:12:20,160 --> 01:12:21,160
究竟去了哪儿？
Where could she have gone?

736
01:12:40,850 --> 01:12:42,780
你不如去其他地方找找
Why don't you look somewhere else?

737
01:12:43,350 --> 01:12:44,720
次子不要有事
Please let Mei be all right.

738
01:12:48,190 --> 01:12:50,106
次子，我不该骂你的
Mei, I shouldn't have scolded you.

739
01:12:50,190 --> 01:12:54,576
你原谅我，你不要有事呀
Please forgive me. Please be all right.

740
01:12:54,660 --> 01:12:56,060
次子
Mei!

741
01:13:16,920 --> 01:13:18,110
停车
Stop!

742
01:13:20,890 --> 01:13:22,606
你神经病，撞死你的
Are you crazy? You could've killed yourself!

743
01:13:22,690 --> 01:13:24,046
我在找妹妹
I'm looking for my sister.

744
01:13:24,130 --> 01:13:25,242
有见过小女孩经过吗？
Have you seen a little girl pass by?

745
01:13:26,490 --> 01:13:27,716
小女孩？
A little girl?

746
01:13:27,800 --> 01:13:29,090
可能去了七国山医院
She may have gone to Shichikokuyama Hospital.

747
01:13:29,730 --> 01:13:30,960
我妹妹只有四岁
My sister is only four years old.

748
01:13:31,800 --> 01:13:32,800
你有留意吗？
Did you happen to notice her?

749
01:13:34,200 --> 01:13:36,416
我们是由七国山来的
We came from Shichikokuyama,

750
01:13:36,500 --> 01:13:38,670
但是沿路上都不见有小女孩经过
but we didn't see any little girl along the way.

751
01:13:40,140 --> 01:13:41,700
是，多谢你们
Yes, thank you very much.

752
01:13:42,740 --> 01:13:43,740
你从哪儿来？
Where did you come from?

753
01:13:44,650 --> 01:13:45,726
由龙猫山来
From Totoro Mountain.

754
01:13:45,810 --> 01:13:46,810
龙猫山？
Totoro Mountain?

755
01:13:47,320 --> 01:13:48,836
你没弄错吧，很远的
You must be mistaken. That's very far away.

756
01:13:48,920 --> 01:13:50,280
这么远，你怎样来？
It's so far. How did you get here?

757
01:13:51,820 --> 01:13:52,820
那你慢慢找吧
Well, good luck finding her.

758
01:14:03,470 --> 01:14:04,470
草子
Satsuki!

759
01:14:06,570 --> 01:14:07,970
害羞仔，找到吗？
Kanta, did you find her?

760
01:14:09,770 --> 01:14:11,070
还没有，里面都没有
Not yet. She's not in there.

761
01:14:12,670 --> 01:14:14,110
爸爸他们在四周寻找
My dad and the others are looking around.

762
01:14:14,740 --> 01:14:16,110
我和你去七国山找吧
I'll go to Shichikokuyama with you.

763
01:14:16,750 --> 01:14:18,370
现在你先回家，好嘛
You go on home first, okay?

764
01:14:19,080 --> 01:14:20,810
次子一定是去医院时
Mei must've

765
01:14:20,880 --> 01:14:22,210
在路上迷了途
gotten lost on the way to the hospital.

766
01:14:24,090 --> 01:14:25,810
他们刚才在河边找到一只鞋子
A little while ago, they found a shoe by the river.

767
01:14:33,800 --> 01:14:35,520
你快去河边看看是不是次子的
Go check by the river and see if it's Mei's!

768
01:14:53,620 --> 01:14:54,620
还没找到
Not yet.

769
01:15:06,290 --> 01:15:07,850
次子，你不要死呀
Mei, don't die!

770
01:15:14,800 --> 01:15:16,360
次子，你千万不要死
Mei, please don't die.

771
01:15:27,020 --> 01:15:29,510
南无阿弥陀佛⋯
Namu Amida Butsu…

772
01:15:31,220 --> 01:15:33,780
在那儿，你们快过去那边打捞
Over there! Hurry and drag that side!

773
01:15:44,730 --> 01:15:45,630
南无阿弥陀佛⋯
Namu Amida Butsu…

774
01:15:45,730 --> 01:15:46,860
草子正赶来
The Kusakabes are on their way.

775
01:15:52,040 --> 01:15:53,040
次子
Mei!

776
01:15:54,640 --> 01:15:56,040
我们找到次子的鞋子
We found Mei's shoe.

777
01:16:05,550 --> 01:16:06,950
这鞋子不是次子的
It's not Mei's.

778
01:16:17,670 --> 01:16:21,416
菩萨有灵，幸好不是次子的
Thank goodness, it wasn't Mei's.

779
01:16:21,500 --> 01:16:22,500
吓死我了
You gave me such a scare.

780
01:16:23,000 --> 01:16:24,300
原来那鞋子不是小孩子的
So that sandal wasn't a child's after all.

781
01:16:24,970 --> 01:16:27,460
不用找了，摆乌龙
You can stop looking. It was all a mistake.

782
01:16:28,410 --> 01:16:30,380
她没有掉进水
She didn't fall into the water.

783
01:16:31,210 --> 01:16:32,210
那就好了⋯
That's a relief…

784
01:16:32,980 --> 01:16:34,110
真是吓死呀⋯
What a scare…

785
01:16:47,730 --> 01:16:50,060
草子，你去哪儿？
Satsuki, where are you going?

786
01:17:07,120 --> 01:17:09,936
求求你们，让我见龙猫
Please, let me see Totoro.

787
01:17:10,020 --> 01:17:12,820
次子迷了途，天就快黑
Mei is lost, and it's getting dark.

788
01:17:12,920 --> 01:17:14,860
但是我们还没找到她
But we still haven't found her.

789
01:17:46,860 --> 01:17:47,860
龙猫
Totoro!

790
01:17:49,890 --> 01:17:52,306
龙猫，次子迷了途
Totoro, Mei is lost.

791
01:17:52,390 --> 01:17:53,876
我老是找不到她
I just can't find her.

792
01:17:53,960 --> 01:17:55,760
求求你，帮我找她
Please, help me find her.

793
01:17:57,270 --> 01:17:59,530
她一定是不知躲在哪儿在哭
I'm sure she's crying somewhere.

794
01:18:00,870 --> 01:18:03,130
我现在都不知道怎么办
I don't know what to do.

795
01:19:02,230 --> 01:19:03,230
原来是只猫巴士
It's a Catbus!

796
01:19:37,670 --> 01:19:38,690
请小心车门
Please watch the doors.

797
01:19:38,770 --> 01:19:41,659
Please Stand　clear of door
Please stand clear of the doors.

798
01:20:15,900 --> 01:20:17,770
次子
Mei.

799
01:20:27,420 --> 01:20:28,810
树都避开
Even the trees are getting out of the way!

800
01:21:02,080 --> 01:21:03,180
次子
Mei!

801
01:21:06,350 --> 01:21:07,550
姐姐呀
Satsuki!

802
01:21:10,460 --> 01:21:12,090
姐姐呀
Satsuki!

803
01:21:22,683 --> 01:21:23,516
次子
Mei!

804
01:21:23,600 --> 01:21:24,700
次子
Mei!

805
01:21:24,770 --> 01:21:26,140
姐姐
Satsuki!

806
01:21:29,110 --> 01:21:30,340
傻瓜，我很担心你
You silly girl, I was so worried about you.

807
01:21:30,410 --> 01:21:31,670
对不起
I'm sorry.

808
01:21:34,380 --> 01:21:36,710
你想将粟米送去医院给妈咪吃？
Did you want to take the corn to the hospital for Mom?

809
01:21:49,500 --> 01:21:50,930
你送我们去医院？
You'll take us to the hospital?

810
01:21:54,300 --> 01:21:55,300
真好
That's great!

811
01:22:05,110 --> 01:22:07,836
对不起，因为医生要我提前出院
I'm sorry. The doctor says I can leave the hospital early,

812
01:22:07,920 --> 01:22:11,580
我很心急，所以打电报给你们
so I was so excited, I sent you a telegram.

813
01:22:12,620 --> 01:22:14,140
吓了你们，真不好意思
I'm sorry I gave you such a scare.

814
01:22:14,920 --> 01:22:18,690
如果孩子知道⋯你明天可以出院
If the girls knew you could leave the hospital tomorrow,

815
01:22:18,760 --> 01:22:20,246
我想她们一定很开心
I'm sure they'd be very happy.

816
01:22:20,330 --> 01:22:21,630
她们希望你出院好久了
They've been hoping for you to come home for so long.

817
01:22:23,930 --> 01:22:25,130
我住了医院这么久
I've been in the hospital such a long time,

818
01:22:25,230 --> 01:22:27,170
使她们受了很多苦
and they've had to go through so much.

819
01:22:27,240 --> 01:22:29,860
没人照顾她们，我心里很难过
It breaks my heart not being there to take care of them.

820
01:22:31,770 --> 01:22:32,770
她们很懂事
They're such good girls.

821
01:22:33,440 --> 01:22:34,670
我出院后
Once I'm out of the hospital,

822
01:22:34,740 --> 01:22:37,270
她们两个就不用那么辛苦
those two won't have to work so hard anymore.

823
01:22:38,050 --> 01:22:40,170
不辛苦，她们整天都说
Oh, they don't mind. They're always saying

824
01:22:40,250 --> 01:22:41,770
要找龙猫送药来医好你
they'll find Totoro and have him bring medicine to make you well.

825
01:22:43,450 --> 01:22:44,920
孩子们真是天真
Children really are so innocent.

826
01:22:46,250 --> 01:22:47,976
妈咪好像没事了
Mom looks all better now.

827
01:22:48,060 --> 01:22:49,476
还精神很好
She seems full of energy, too.

828
01:22:49,560 --> 01:22:50,560
是呀
Yeah.

829
01:22:59,000 --> 01:23:00,786
我好像吃了龙猫的药那么精神
I feel so full of energy, like I took Totoro's medicine.

830
01:23:00,870 --> 01:23:01,870
是吗？
Really?

831
01:23:10,510 --> 01:23:14,500
有条粟米，是谁拿来呢？
Who brought this corn here?

832
01:23:15,680 --> 01:23:17,106
莫非她们真的找到龙猫
Maybe they really did find Totoro,

833
01:23:17,190 --> 01:23:18,410
送粟米来给我治病
and brought me this corn to make me well.

834
01:23:21,990 --> 01:23:24,050
我想可能是，你看看
I think maybe they did. Look.

835
01:23:25,330 --> 01:23:26,920
我们最疼你
We love you very much.

